            <obo:IAO_0000115>A deficiency of the essential metal Zinc; an     
  essential cofactor for many enzymes. Zinc deficiency is caused by a lack of 
  zinc in the diet, loss of zinc after absorption, for example through loss   
  through burns, inability to absorb Zinc, or increased loss through exercise.
  </obo:IAO_0000115>                                                          
            <obo:IAO_0000117>Helen Parkinson</obo:IAO_0000117>                
            <efo:definition_citation>https://en.wikipedia.                    
